Package org.opendaylight.yang.gen.v1.urn.opendaylight.params.xml.ns.yang.ncadaptor.rev150105.get.node.instance.output

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NodeCfgData
    <p>This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module <b>ncadaptor</b> <br>(Source path: <i>META-INF/yang/ncadaptor.yang</i>): <pre> container node-cfg-data { leaf jsonURI { type string; } } </pre> The schema path to identify an instance is <i>ncadaptor/get-node-instance/output/node-cfg-data</i> <p>To create instances of this class use NodeCfgDataBuilder.
    NodeOperData
    Operational information about the device <p>This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module <b>ncadaptor</b> <br>(Source path: <i>META-INF/yang/ncadaptor.yang</i>): <pre> container node-oper-data { leaf oper-node { type boolean; } leaf device-name { type string; } leaf device-family { type string; } leaf yang-revision { type string; } leaf deviceVendor { type string; } leaf deviceOS { type string; } leaf deviceOSVersion { type string; } leaf json-url { type string; } } </pre> The schema path to identify an instance is <i>ncadaptor/get-node-instance/output/node-oper-data</i> <p>To create instances of this class use NodeOperDataBuilder.
  • Class Summary

    NodeOperDataBuilder
